The '''Royal Residence''' was the [[Queen Mother]]'s personal quarters in the [[Fountain Palace]] on [[Hapes/Legends|Hapes]]. The entrance was a long corridor, at the front of which were a dozen royal guards and an immense [[wind-crystal]] chandelier.

